      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, thank you. One last thing—in cases where there's a deficiency, is it usually because the B12 isn't there at all, or is it something else causing the B12 to be lost or \"missing\" from the system? I'm trying to understand if it's a lack of intake or a failure of the body to retain what is consumed.",
